      "content": "The Operational Hub has two pricing tiers:\n\n**Starter ($750/month)**\n- Designed for early-stage teams\n- Includes entity formation, financial operations\n- Up to 5 invoices per month\n\n**Standard ($1,250/month + $250/contributor)**\n- For growing teams of 3+ contributors\n- Adds contributor onboarding, multi-currency payouts\n- Dedicated ops support, expense policies\n- Unlimited invoicing\n\n**Advanced & Custom** tier exists for scaling organizations: multiple entity support, dedicated account manager, admin portal, custom workflows. Add-ons available for exchange setup, banking, AML monitoring.\n\nThis is significant because it represents Powerhouse's first concrete, recurring revenue model with clear unit economics. A team of 10 contributors on Standard = $1,250 + $2,500 = $3,750/month per customer. Scaling to 20 customers = $75,000 MRR.",
